Dayton Bar Association v. Callahan.

[Cite as Dayton Bar Assn. v. Callahan (1988), 37 Ohio St. 3d 601.]

No. D.D. 87-19 Submitted June 1, 1988 Decided June 29, 1988.)

The application for reinstatement to the practice of law is granted. J. Gerard Callahan, Jr., is reinstated to the practice of law in the state of Ohio.

(For earlier case, see [1988], 36 Ohio St. 3d 179, 522 N.E. 2d 542.)

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur,
